' Sample 02: Using a Variable.BAS
' 
' This sample demonstrates how to use a simple string variable.
' 
' The "message" variable is assigned a string, itself passed to the
' MsgBox Visual Basic function to display a message box with this message.
'
' For more details, please refer to the PADS Layout Visual Basic Editor Help File.
'
Sub Main
	message = "Hi, how are you?"
	MsgBox message
End Sub
